[l] Das Weisse Haus scheint bemueht, systematisch die Presse zu delegitimieren. Die Methode funktioniert so:The incident reflects an emerging pattern noted by several top political reporters in how the Trump administration handles its most controversial policy proposals, and undermines the press in the process:Wait for a draft memo of a proposal to be leaked to the press.Refuse to comment when asked about the draft.Wait to dispute a story's accuracy until the story is published.Accuse the press of never having sought comment to begin with.Achtet mal drauf, ob euch sowas demnaechst auch hier auffaellt.
